  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Nexus is a collaboration between academic institutions, advocacy and industry to answer
      important questions about narcolepsy. It is a web-based observational study of
      patient-reported outcomes in adult patients with narcolepsy, with follow-up every six months.

      Nexus website: www.narcolepsyregistry.com
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
